import React, { useState } from "react"; import style from "../assets/style.module.css"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import axios from "axios"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const Register = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [form, setForm] = useState({ nama: "", email: "", phone: "", password: "", image: "", }); const onSubmitHandler = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); console.log(form); if ( form.nama === "" || form.email === "" || form.phone === "" || form.password === "" ) { alert("Please fill all the field"); } else { const body = { nama: form.nama, email: form.email, phone: form.phone, password: form.password, image: form.image, }; axios .post(`${process.env.REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL}/user/register`, body) .then((res) => { console.log(res.data); alert("Register success"); }) .catch((err) => { console.log(err); }); } }; return (
onSubmitHandler(e)}>
